name: The eyemakine
description:
The orbital device circles in infinite cycles. It has no mainframe.
Once the emission started, everthing seemed to be out of no known source,
and what was once stainless became blue, purple and organik. The outcomes
started to float from the main turbine. Once this selected rainbow-like
substance began pouring, that's when all the bends and leaps started to
happen. Could only watch it from a distance, trying to understand its
new shapes and movements, but the ripples went slowly getting to my 
vision, from a distance. Small portalized holes, gave space to a branched
biome that took control of the mid-frame, making it more and more burstable.
There was no coming back, no return. It was now under a new flux, a different
existance to what it was for so long, its immeasurable stillness. The eyemakine.
